    "By analyzing existing shapes, the model learns basic features and principles about the objects with which we are training.",
    "In many cases, the operator is allowed to set multiple variables to force the desired characteristic on the generated object.",
    "Most of these methods work with point clouds since their unordered nature ensures that the models generate the coordinates of each point independently, but the relationship between neighboring points is maintained.",
